task.summary: Added basic JavaFX MainWindow, MenuBar and AboutDialog as well as Controller classes and Window Event handling
Updated AboutDialog, MainMenuBar and added MainToolBar
Added default file name for Save Dialogs
Added Method to Clear ArtBoard (remove it entirely)
- Added ToolTips to Toolbar - Added Toolbar and Status Bar MenuItems to View Menu
Ensure event is within artboard boundaries
Fixed a bug where MenuBar could be hidden using ALT
Adjusted stroke width and resize anchor dimensions
Last drawn object is automatically selected at mouse released event
Fixed a bug where resize anchors would not stay attached to focus rectangle
Resize now works with all four resize anchors
Rectangles and Ellipses are now properly resizable
Selection now stays persistent even when switching tools
SE Resize now sticks to boundaries
Added selection and binding of lines to FocusOutline
Changed Design of Resize Anchors slightly
Added first attempt of rotating shapes
Focus Outline is now set to correct rotation when shape is deselected and reselected
First attempt of (nun functional) History Keeping (Undo/Redo)
